## Challenge

Use the paste() function to concatenate the strings “hello” and “there” in R.

## Solution

```r
paste("hello","there")
```

```output
[1] "hello there"
```

HTML <div>

## Challenge

Use the paste() function to concatenate the strings “hello” and “there” in R.

## School Solution

```r
paste("hello","there")
```

```output
[1] "hello there"
```

Great! Now use paste0() function to paste together “mono” and “rail” to make “monorail”

<div class="solution">

## Fast Solution

```r
paste0("mono","rail")
```

```output
[1] "monorail"
```
